headline: Enphase Energy (NasdaqGM:ENPH) Sees 7% Dip As Latest Earnings Report Shows Sales and Income Drop
summary: Enphase Energy (NasdaqGM:ENPH) recently announced an increase in the deployment of solutions for legacy NEM solar systems and launched the IQ Battery 5P, yet its stock price fell by 7% over the last month. The decline comes despite Enphase's initiative to support homeowners with energy demands in California and its expansion of grid services programs.
